ager container ya kisi or cheez ki width bari krni hai tw width ka istamal karo

ager height apne hisab se deni hai tw height ka istamal karo


ager kisi content ya box ya container ko ander kheech na hai tw padding use karo padding ander kiyor cheezon ko khech ta hai

ager kisi content ya box ya container ko bhar kiyo krna hai tw margin use karo margin bhar kiyor cheezon ko phek ta hai

border ager kisi box per border dena hai tw border istamal karo or ager os border ko ko thora ghuma hai tw border radious dedo osse

ager kisi ccheez ki visisblyty kam ya zyada krni hai tw z-index ka istamal karo





font ko ager apne hisab se bara ya chota kr na hai tw font-size use karo


font ko ager dark ya light krna hai tw font-weight istamal karo


font ager apni marzi ka lagana hai like stylish ya sada tw font-family use karo


text ager center end ya start me lana hai tw text-align use karo


text ko ager underline ya or bhi alag kisam ki decoration wagera krni hai tw font-decoration istalam karo






