position absoulute and relative ek sath use hoti hain
absolute se app kisi bhi ccheez ko move kara sakte hain kaaheen bhi jese manlo ek box hai app chate ho os k ander jo box haai wo parent box k top me ajai tw app parent box ko relaative  doge take jo box ko apne absolute dya hai wo body k top me nhi parent k top me aii






